                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-111-victim999 t18320906-111-viclabel631"></join>. On the 18th of July the prisoner walked about six feet into my shop, and took a piece of print; she ran out - I and my assistant followed her; she partly dropped the print on the pavement, but held one end of it still under her arm and dragged it into the shop with her.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320906-111-person1001">
                  THOMAS 
                  ROBSON
