                  </persName>
            . I am assistant to the prosecutor. On the 18th of July about nine o'clock in the evening, the prisoner came into the shop: there was another person very near to her, and they both entered at the same time - the prisoner took the print, and walked out; I followed and brought her back.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined by MR. PHILLIPS. Q. How near were you to her? A. About three yards; I am sure she dropped it.</p>
